title: DS310.24 Joins | DataStax Enterprise 6 Search
description:
#DataStaxAcademy #DS310
DS310.24 Joins
In this section we will review how joins are not possible in Cassandra. However, with the addition of search indexes in DSE Search, this means that certain joins are now feasible.

ASK QUESTIONS at https://community.datastax.com -- where experts from DataStax & the Apache Cassandra community share their expertise everyday.
